lead_paragraph: Tottenham Hotspur are in a "tough period" due to their new stadium project, team manager Mauricio Pochettino said, citing the experience of rival team Arsenal, who also suffered after the switch to the Emirates Stadium.

headline.print_headline: Spurs in a 'Tough Period', Says Pochettino Ahead of Stadium Move
